{"tid":2373810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"結果最尾侵都冇特赦到阿桑奇同斯諾登","createTime":"2021-01-20T18:03:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T02:49:50.000Z","uid":105798,"like":6,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"39d0cd55a32336b30116deb06ec8cb393ecb19d8","tid":2373810,"uid":105798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T18:03:50.000Z","msg":"為咗佢衝入國會班人都冇份<br />\n<br />\n咁佢特赦咗咩人?<br />\n共和黨大金主<br />\nOne pardon recipients was Elliott Broidy, a prominent Republican fundraiser who pleaded guilty last fall in a scheme to lobby the Trump administration to drop an investigation into the looting of a Malaysian wealth fund. <br />\n女婿個朋友<br />\nAnother was Ken Kurson, a friend of Trump son-in-law Jared Kushner who was charged last October with cyberstalking during a heated divorce. <br />\n盟友個前夫<br />\nHours later, the White House announced one last pardon, for Al Pirro, the ex-husband of Trump ally Jeanine Pirro, a Fox News Channel host. Al Pirro had been convicted in 2000 of tax charges.<br />\n國師班農<br />\nBannon&rsquo;s pardon was especially notable given that the prosecution was still in its early stages and any trial was months away. Whereas pardon recipients are conventionally thought of as defendants who have faced justice, often by having served at least some prison time, the pardon nullifies the prosecution and effectively eliminates any prospect for punishment. <br />\n仲有rappers...<br />\nAmong them were rappers Lil Wayne and Kodak Black, both convicted in Florida on weapons charges. Wayne, whose real name is Dwayne Michael Carter, has frequently expressed support for Trump and recently met with the president on criminal justice issues. Kodak Black, also known as Bill K. Kapri, had his sentence commuted.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://apnews.com/article/steve-bannon-trump-pardons-broidy-66c82f25134735e742b2501c118723bb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fsteve-bannon-trump-pardons-broidy-66c82f25134735e742b2501c118723bb&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia7PGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=d560b05b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apnews.com/article/steve-bannon-trump-pardons-broidy-66c82f25134735e742b2501c118723bb</a>"},{"pid":"bd71cd6cf5694103bdc2d64bd373d96f04ec9aa4","tid":2373810,"uid":105798,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T18:05:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Timcast/status/1351871518737903619\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTimcast%2Fstatus%2F1351871518737903619&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia7PGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=41937759\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTimcast%2Fstatus%2F1351871518737903619&h=d9c916c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Timcast/status/1351871518737903619</a>"},{"pid":"c81241df8b541551985ba41985249f3ce8743f30","tid":2373810,"uid":237459,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T18:06:06.000Z","msg":"侵同共和黨咪又係得把口<br />\n佢哋以後都唔會贏到"},{"pid":"5634444439a559ed3b59f87ae4481567d7d9ba78","tid":2373810,"uid":105798,"like":9,"dislike":12,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T18:08:21.000Z","msg":"信咗佢衝入國會個班變晒condoms"},{"pid":"31122ad8dcf425968e3ca99dc833ac000367141a","tid":2373810,"uid":337336,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T18:09:48.000Z","msg":"為咗佢衝入國會班人有份咪話畀人知佢自己煽動？on9"},{"pid":"c2fec03bac2bd1f1fb3d205f01147ce5a0f5b446","tid":2373810,"uid":237459,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5634444439a559ed3b59f87ae4481567d7d9ba78","tid":2373810,"uid":105798,"like":9,"dislike":12,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T18:08:21.000Z","msg":"信咗佢衝入國會個班變晒condoms"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T18:10:12.000Z","msg":"大送頭"},{"pid":"becbbedef1edb19cda9323230d491d59ee4b7b8c","tid":2373810,"uid":105798,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"31122ad8dcf425968e3ca99dc833ac000367141a","tid":2373810,"uid":337336,"like